node.title: Search for swimmer missing at Auckland beach paused
node.description: The middle-aged man was reported missing at Karioitahi Beach on Auckland's west coast last night.
node.content:
["The search for a swimmer missing at Karioitahi Beach on Auckland's west coast has been paused.", "", "
File pic Photo: Auckland Council
", "The middle-aged man was reported missing at 8.15pm last night and a search was launched until it became too dark to continue.", "Lifeguards, the police Eagle helicopter and a Coastguard air patrol carried out a shoreline sweep this morning but found no sign of him.", "It is not yet known whether the search will resume tomorrow.", "There have been at least 30 water-related deaths since the beginning of December."]
